@startuml
!theme plain
skinparam SequenceMessageAlign center
skinparam linetype ortho

title Sơ đồ tuần tự: Đánh giá sản phẩm (Product Review)

actor "Khách hàng" as Customer
boundary "UI (Giao diện chi tiết sản phẩm)" as UI
control ReviewController
control ReviewService
entity ReviewDao
participant "ReviewCreatedEventPublisher" as Publisher
participant "ProductReviewStatsObserver" as Observer
database "Database" as DB

Customer -> UI : Gửi biểu mẫu đánh giá\n(Số sao, Nội dung)
activate UI

UI -> ReviewController : HTTP POST /api/v1/reviews\n(JSON: CreateReviewRequest)
activate ReviewController

ReviewController -> ReviewController : Phân giải danh tính khách hàng\n(Từ JwtAuthenticationFilter)

ReviewController -> ReviewService : createReview(userId, requestDTO)
activate ReviewService

' 1. Logic nghiệp vụ & Lưu trữ
ReviewService -> ReviewService : Khởi tạo thực thể Review\n(Gán User, Product, Rating, Comment)

ReviewService -> ReviewDao : save(review)
activate ReviewDao
ReviewDao -> DB : INSERT INTO reviews
activate DB
DB --> ReviewDao : Success
deactivate DB
ReviewDao --> ReviewService : Saved Review
deactivate ReviewDao

' 2. Observer Pattern - Event Publishing
ReviewService -> Publisher : publishReviewCreated(review)
activate Publisher

Publisher -> Observer : onReviewCreated(review)
activate Observer

Observer -> ReviewDao : calculateAverageRatingByProductId(productId)
activate ReviewDao
ReviewDao -> DB : SELECT AVG(rating) FROM reviews
activate DB
DB --> ReviewDao : Average Rating Value
deactivate DB
ReviewDao --> Observer : Trả về số sao trung bình
deactivate ReviewDao

Observer -> ReviewDao : countByProductId(productId)
activate ReviewDao
ReviewDao -> DB : SELECT COUNT(*) FROM reviews
activate DB
DB --> ReviewDao : Review Count
deactivate DB
ReviewDao --> Observer : Trả về tổng lượt đánh giá
deactivate ReviewDao

Observer -> Observer : Cập nhật lại mức sao trung bình\ncho sản phẩm (Log/Cache Update)
Observer --> Publisher : Hoàn tất cập nhật
deactivate Observer

Publisher --> ReviewService : Thông báo hoàn tất sự kiện
deactivate Publisher

' 3. Response
ReviewService --> ReviewController : Trả về ReviewResponse (DTO)
deactivate ReviewService

ReviewController --> UI : HTTP 201 Created (JSON Response)
deactivate ReviewController

UI --> Customer : Hiển thị đánh giá mới vừa tạo
deactivate UI

@enduml
